thread.title: A dramatic death, but few clues from Austin bomber suspect

title: A dramatic death, but few clues from Austin bomber suspect
text:
A dramatic death, but few clues from Austin bomber suspect Wednesday, March 21, 2018 - 01:57 
Police say they tracked the suspected Austin bomber, 23-year-old Mark Conditt, for a day before closing in on him on the side of a highway where he blew himself up early Wednesday.
